content:
The Commercial line of business gives you a fully functional example of the Commercial Auto product models, rating procedures, and business processes for quoting and issuing policies.

You can use the models and processes as a reference to develop your own product models and business processes or extend them and make them your own.

Product Models and Rating Procedures
The product model and the rating procedure calculate prices for Commercial Auto at runtime.
Business Processes
To use these features, you need a Property and Casualty org.

Commercial Auto Product Model
A single-instance product model that lets businesses create quotes for multiple vehicles tied to a single location.

Commercial Auto Rating
Pricing services use the product model data, product rating procedure, and pricing formulas to price coverages, vehicles, and total premium.

Commercial Quote Business Process
A quote business process created as an example for General Liability, which can be used and extended to create own business processes.
title: Commercial Auto Insurance with OmniStudio Overview
